(1, '<h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 17px; background-color: rgb(239, 247, 249);\">Clubhead Design</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; position: relative; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 22px; background-color: rgb(239, 247, 249);\">The larger club head of these fairway woods, combined with a shallow face design, offers a distinct advantage for all golfers. Rupesh</p>', 'banner-29494.png', 1, '2024-02-19 04:03:57', '2024-02-19 08:33:38'),
(2, '<h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 17px; background-color: rgb(239, 247, 249);\">Optimal Control</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; position: relative; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 22px; background-color: rgb(239, 247, 249);\">Have better control with a smaller 183cc club head. A smaller club head with better swing impact at the right position.</p>', 'banner-51733.png', 1, '2024-02-19 04:04:10', '2024-02-19 04:04:10'),
(3, '<h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 17px; background-color: rgb(239, 247, 249);\">Distance off the Fairway &amp; Tee</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; position: relative; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 22px; background-color: rgb(239, 247, 249);\">Make the most of your distance with just a 10.5-degree lofted 2 wood. The swing is exactly the same as when using your 3 wood.</p>', 'banner-28330.png', 1, '2024-02-19 04:04:25', '2024-02-19 04:04:25'),
(4, '<h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 17px; background-color: rgb(239, 247, 249);\">Accuracy</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; position: relative; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 22px; background-color: rgb(239, 247, 249);\">Many golfers choose to utilize a 3w instead of their driver because they lack confidence in it. You can increase distance with a 2-wood with accuracy.</p>', 'banner-94462.png', 1, '2024-02-19 04:04:38', '2024-02-19 04:04:38'),
(5, '<h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 17px; background-color: rgb(239, 247, 249);\">Shot Shaping and Versatility</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; position: relative; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 22px; background-color: rgb(239, 247, 249);\">Adjustable lower loft swing and clubhead design for long, and straight shots.</p>', 'banner-13699.png', 1, '2024-02-19 04:04:52', '2024-02-19 04:04:52'),
(6, '<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(239, 247, 249); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><b>Forgiveness</b></span><br></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; position: relative; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 22px; background-color: rgb(239, 247, 249);\">Forgiveness on off-center hits is a crucial feature that golfers can rely on to preserve their distance and accuracy.</p>', 'banner-72073.png', 1, '2024-02-19 04:05:25', '2024-02-25 23:42:57');
